<p begin="5298800000t" end="5323600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle138">dan terima apa saja ujian.</p>
<p begin="5331200000t" end="5361200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle139">[muzik sayu]</p>
<p begin="5369200000t" end="5383600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle140">Awak kena terima.</p>
<p begin="5388400000t" end="5419200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle141">Awak kena terima segala<br/>ujian ini dengan hati terbuka.</p>
<p begin="5424800000t" end="5438400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle142">Tanpa rasa dendam.</p>
<p begin="5442800000t" end="5470800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle143">Dan jangan soalkan sebab awak di sini.</p>
<p begin="5485200000t" end="5499600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle144">Maksud Ustaz...</p>
<p begin="5508400000t" end="5555600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle145">saya kena terima yang<br/>saya akan jadi pelacur selamanya?</p>
<p begin="5574000000t" end="5588800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle146">Bukan itu maksud saya.</p>
<p begin="5616000000t" end="5629600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle147">Awak kena berjuang.</p>
<p begin="5637600000t" end="5651600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle148">Hukum tetap hukum.</p>
<p begin="5659600000t" end="5686800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle149">Di situlah ujian sebenar.</p>
<p begin="5725200000t" end="5751600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle150">Langkah pertama awak kena terima.</p>
<p begin="5756000000t" end="5776800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle151">Terima ujian dalam hidup awak.</p>
<p begin="5801600000t" end="5833200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle152">Selama kita tak reda<br/>dengan ujian Allah untuk kita,</p>
<p begin="5865200000t" end="5914800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle153">selama itu kita akan salahkan Allah<br/>yang tak pernah berlaku adil.</p>
<p begin="5926800000t" end="5952000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle154">Allah Maha Adil.</p>
<p begin="5978400000t" end="6000000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle155">Mungkin di dunia, awak susah.</p>
<p begin="6012400000t" end="6040800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle156">Tapi di akhirat nanti,<br/>jika awak lalui ujian ini,</p>
<p begin="6059200000t" end="6087200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle157">Insya-Allah, makam awak lebih<br/>tinggi daripada para wali.</p>
<p begin="6113200000t" end="6144800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle158">Dengan syarat awak ikhlas<br/>dengan ujian hidup awak.</p>
<p begin="6149600000t" end="6166400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle159">Allah Maha Adil.</p>
<p begin="6186000000t" end="6214000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle160">Dia berhak lakukan apa yang Dia mahu.</p>
<p begin="6228800000t" end="6249200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle161">Itu erti keadilan.</p>
<p begin="6280800000t" end="6310000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle162">Kebesaran-Nya tiada tandingan.</p>
<p begin="6317200000t" end="6329600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle163">[ketawa kecil]</p>
<p begin="6366400000t" end="6380000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle164">Sudah lama...</p>
<p begin="6392800000t" end="6420400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle165">saya cari jawapan tentang keadilan Allah.</p>
<p begin="6433600000t" end="6456000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle166">Hari ini saya faham yang...</p>
<p begin="6468800000t" end="6487600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle167">adil itu reda.</p>
<p begin="6508400000t" end="6525200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle168">Reda dengan ketentuan-Nya.</p>
<p begin="6550400000t" end="6560800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle169">Terima kasih, Ustaz.</p>
<p begin="6570400000t" end="6591200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle170">Bersusah-payah mencari jawapan untuk saya.</p>
