<p begin="8291200000t" end="8306000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle214">Dalam hidup saya...</p>
<p begin="8320400000t" end="8350400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle215">saya pernah kenal beberapa orang lelaki...</p>
<p begin="8362400000t" end="8389600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle216">yang berkata mereka boleh ubah hidup saya.</p>
<p begin="8397200000t" end="8410800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle217">Rupanya tidak.</p>
<p begin="8435200000t" end="8458000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle218">Lelaki pertama yang saya kenal...</p>
<p begin="8464000000t" end="8481600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle219">sewaktu saya berumur 17 tahun.</p>
<p begin="8487600000t" end="8501200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle220"><span style="style.center_1">Nama dia Marzuki.</span></p>
<p begin="8508400000t" end="8555200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle221"><span style="style.center_1">Dia tiada kerja tetap</span><br/><span style="style.center_1">tapi dia ajak saya kahwin.</span></p>
<p begin="8560800000t" end="8594800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle222"><span style="style.center_1">Saya fikir,"Apabila saya bersama dia,</span><br/><span style="style.center_1">nasib saya akan berubah."</span></p>
<p begin="8598400000t" end="8612400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle223">Saya bawa dia jumpa mak saya.</p>
<p begin="8616400000t" end="8649600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle224">Mak, ini Marzuki. Kawan saya.</p>
<p begin="8692000000t" end="8701200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle225">Hai.</p>
<p begin="8717200000t" end="8727200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle226">Hai.</p>
<p begin="8732000000t" end="8752400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle227"><span style="style.center_1">Rupa-rupanya dia yang berubah.</span></p>
<p begin="8758400000t" end="8779200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle228"><span style="style.center_1">Dia jatuh hati dengan mak saya.</span></p>
<p begin="8798000000t" end="8839200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle229">Dan tiba-tiba, sekarang dia<br/>yang menjual saya dan mak saya.</p>
<p begin="8855200000t" end="8866800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle230">Pelik bukan?</p>
