<p begin="10512400000t" end="10522400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle274">Um...</p>
<p begin="10524800000t" end="10555600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle275">Sudah pukul berapa?<br/>Sudah masuk waktu Subuh bukan?</p>
<p begin="10564400000t" end="10578800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle276">Awak tak pergi ke masjid?</p>
<p begin="10600000000t" end="10611600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle277">Mari.</p>
<p begin="10646800000t" end="10667200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle278">Saya dengar doa awak tempoh hari.</p>
