<p begin="10709200000t" end="10737200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle280">Tempoh hari. Selepas awak solat.</p>
<p begin="10753600000t" end="10799200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle281">Apabila awak cakap tiada satu pun<br/>doa awak yang Allah makbulkan.</p>
